# {{name}}

An agent demonstrating custom tool integrations, powered by Claude and Castari. This template shows how to build and integrate your own tools using the MCP (Model Context Protocol) pattern.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Deploy to Castari
cast deploy

# Invoke the agent
cast invoke {{name}} "What's 15% of 250?"
```

## Local Development

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Run locally
echo "What's the weather in San Francisco?" | npm run dev

# Build for production
npm run build
```

## Example Tool Usage

```bash
# Calculator
echo "Calculate 2^10 and sqrt(144)" | npm run dev

